Bring 4 to 6 quarts of water to a rolling boil, add salt to taste and the Penne, and stir gently. Cook pasta according to package directions adding the vegetables and peas for the last 4 minutes of cooking; remove from heat and drain well. Meanwhile, in a large pot bring the Traditional Basil Pesto and half-and-half* to a low simmer. Add pasta to the sauce in pot; heat through. Serve topped with Parmesan cheese.